<tr valign="top" height="400" >
<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="1" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.12px; background: white;">Hi {!Lead.FirstName},<br></span><br></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font face="arial">I’m following up on my previous attempts to provide you with a quote for your business insurance.&nbsp;<br></font><br>I understand that there can be many reasons why you may not be interested right now and I wanted to check if any of these apply to you.<br><br><b>Current policy not due to expire?</b><br><span style="font-size: 12pt;">If you let me know your expiry date for your business insurance policy, I can give you a call nearer the time to arrange your quote.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br><b>Got a quote elsewhere?</b><br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">We can often match like-for-like quotes, so if you let us know the cover levels and the quoted price you have received I can see if we can provide a better quote for you.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br><b>Want no further contact?</b><br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">If you are not interested in receiving a quote, just let me know and I will ensure I don’t contact you again.&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>Alternatively, if you are still&nbsp;<b>interested in proceeding with your quote</b>, reply with the best date and time for me to call you. Alternatively you can give me a ring on&nbsp;<b>01242 808 740</b>.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br><font face="arial"><span style="background-color: white;">Kind regards,</span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font><font face="Arial, sans-serif">{!User.FirstName}<br></font></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Sales Team<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br><font face="Arial, sans-serif">E: salesteam@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></font></span><font style="font-size: 12pt;">T:&nbsp;</font><font style="font-size: 12pt;">01242 808740</font></p>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>